Please make sure you have not installed Chrome by other means in
your Slackware box. This program can install it for you and maintain
it updated afterwards.

To install, after unpacking the files, you need to run the provided install.sh
as root. An uninstall.sh script is also provided.

In order to run this program you need to install the packages Python3, PyGtk,
both available on the stock Slackware distro and gksu from SlackBuilds.org.

Thatâ€™s it!
